PolyLine¶

In [65]:
colors = ['blue','orange',  'red']
for k, community in enumerate(edgeLoc):
    locations = edgeLoc[community]
    for loc in locations:
        line = folium.PolyLine(locations=loc, color=colors[k])
        beijing.add_children(line)
